📌 Project Overview
This project is an end-to-end Power BI Sales & Profit Analysis Dashboard built to analyze global sales performance, profitability, and cost efficiency.

🛠 Tools & Technologies
Power BI
Power Query
DAX
Data Modeling (Star Schema)

📂 Dataset Details
Fact Table: Sales
Dimension Tables: Product, Country, Date

📈 Key Features
Interactive KPIs for Sales, Profit, COGS, and Profit Margin
Sales & Profit trend analysis over time
Country-wise and product-wise performance analysis
COGS vs Profit comparison using combo charts
Dynamic slicers for better data exploration

🧠 Skills Demonstrated
Data Cleaning & Transformation
Star Schema Data Modeling
DAX Measures
Data Visualization & Dashboard Design

